From: GitHub Copilot <copilot@github.com>
Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 22:14:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Remove xcpretty from MoltenVK Makefile to fix build

xcpretty is a build prettifier that can cause compilation failures
when it's not installed or properly configured. Removing it from the
build command allows the build to proceed with standard xcodebuild output.

---
 Makefile | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/Makefile b/Makefile
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/Makefile
+++ b/Makefile
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-macos: fetchDependencies | xcpretty
+macos: fetchDependencies
 	xcodebuild build -project MoltenVKPackaging/MoltenVKPackaging.xcodeproj -scheme "MoltenVK Package (macOS only)" -configuration Release
 
 macos-debug: fetchDependencies
-- 
2.32.0
